>\n可惜,呢隻GAME,外國好多人玩,偏偏淨係香港冇人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多係身在外國既香港人,都同我講呢隻GAME外國係勁多人玩,普遍香港人個STEAM都設定係香港,所以香港人買左,馬上開GAME,幾乎係肯定冇場,因為香港SER根本冇人,已經真係有玩開GAME既人,都已經轉哂SER去其他國家玩,而依家最多人既SER而又唔會太LAG既地方,係轉去台灣泰國日本哈薩克呢D地方既SER玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HdDRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHdDRQ.jpg&h=300ec0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於係香港開CAM開台而又玩呢隻GAME既人,係得我一個台,所以呢隻GAME官方果邊都俾左呢一件twitch台台主先有既SKIN我,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/16665881_781048895392865_7174868728788210755_o.jpg?oh=77d2297321dacb84b71d369393e79c2b&amp;oe=593238E6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F16665881_781048895392865_7174868728788210755_o.jpg%3Foh%3D77d2297321dacb84b71d369393e79c2b%26oe%3D593238E6&h=385eb1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/16797126_781048898726198_8047297476270724355_o.jpg?oh=2f5a4bf342f0bc469c7ca8774e4a607b&amp;oe=5941D525\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F16797126_781048898726198_8047297476270724355_o.jpg%3Foh%3D2f5a4bf342f0bc469c7ca8774e4a607b%26oe%3D5941D525&h=6384d9ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/vHoXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FvHoXA.jpg&h=1fb87b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHk7eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHk7eR.jpg&h=f109db8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面呢個係隨便台Official LINE群,有咩突發消息,開台通知,我都會係呢度公布<br />\n<img src=\"http://qr-official.line.me/L/aqio2VXZLo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqr-official.line.me%2FL%2Faqio2VXZLo.png&h=03fd5638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65cc16cdd1c300ab0f299a217e4b3a6c795e0287","tid":273921,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"